The paper describes algorithms for finding palindromes in strings, which is a problem related to data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC). The algorithms also involve geometric concepts such as symmetry (cs.CG) and combinatorial concepts such as counting (cs.DM) and graph theory (cs.GT).
